evidence.text: PAPERLESS ORDER Requiring Status Update. The Parties have notified the Court that the proposed settlement in this matter was presented to the City Commission in a closed‑door session on November 19, 2024, was approved by City officials, and will now be brought before the City Commission on a public agenda tentatively set for December 3, 2024 for final approval. See [ECF No. 193]. Accordingly, the Parties are directed to jointly file a status update regarding the progress of settlement approval on or before December 4, 2024.
